data.description: This beautiful 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home is move-in ready and situated on a large cul-de-sac lot with stunning views of a pond and preserve. The foyer and formal dining room lead to an open kitchen and living room, perfect for family gatherings and entertaining. The gourmet kitchen boasts 42-inch cabinets, a dual oven, microwave and refrigerator. The first floor features an owner's suite, while the second floor includes a large loft and three additional spacious bedrooms with great size walk-in closets. You can enjoy the enclosed extended sunroom, and the community amenity center with pool, fitness gym, tennis, basketball court and playground is just a short walk away. The location is very convenient, just 15 minutes away from River City Shopping and the hospital. Additionally, it's close to both Kings Bay and Mayport Naval Bases, making for an easy work commute.
